        "name": "Radium",
        "is_free": false,
        "about_the_game": "Radium is a physics-based skill game, featuring unique game controls. A game which avoids any non-essential elements and focuses on the elementary minimum. <br>Navigate the ball through the levels, by controlling with two tractor beams that exert force on the ball. In some levels you need to collect tokens to activate the exit.<br>The polarisation change is simple but challenging. By collecting an item the interface changes to yellow, the ball falls upwards and the tractor beams pushes the ball away.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br>\u2022 130 levels of increasing difficulty<br>\u2022 Unique physics-based game controls<br>\u2022 Automatic zoom and scroll function<br>\u2022 Polarization change<br>\u2022 Pure minimalism",
